description: Welcome to Tropicava Hotel and Resort! Where happiness becomes a true reality. During your stay at Tropicava, you, your comfort, and satisfaction is our number one priority! Our hotel is located on a beachy island so you can have the beach right out your front door! We have excellent service and staff at our beautiful hotel. Our hotel has a variety of amenities such as a pool, beach scenery, a buffet, and more! We are also hiring MR's and we sell ranks!
